The goal here will be to show you
ways that this stage in your life

104
00:06:44,820 --> 00:06:47,980
to strategical build and
boost your credit score.

105
00:06:47,980 --> 00:06:52,020
So down the road when you wanna buy
that car or house, or borrow for

106
00:06:52,020 --> 00:06:56,190
a new business venture, your loan will get
approved at the lowest possible rate and

107
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:58,370
with the best possible terms.

108
00:06:58,370 --> 00:06:59,739
Not a bad goal to strive for.

